---
// Campaign loop: model environment → adversarial testing → evidence → back into model.
---

<figure
  class="loop-diagram"
  aria-label="Campaign loop: model environment, adversarial testing, evidence and fixes"
>
  <div class="loop-svg-wrap">
    <svg
      viewBox="0 0 720 400"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      <defs>
        <marker
          id="loop-arrow"
          viewBox="0 0 10 10"
          refX="9"
          refY="5"
          markerWidth="9"
          markerHeight="9"
          orient="auto"
        >
          <path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" fill="var(--accent)"></path>
        </marker>
      </defs>
      <g fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round">
        <path d="M 460 90 Q 680 175 580 270" marker-end="url(#loop-arrow)"></path>
        <path d="M 470 345 Q 360 395 250 345" marker-end="url(#loop-arrow)"></path>
        <path d="M 140 270 Q 40 175 260 90" marker-end="url(#loop-arrow)"></path>
      </g>
    </svg>

    <div class="loop-label" style="top: 17.5%; left: 50%;">
      <span class="t">Model Environment</span>
      <span class="s">production workflows, tools, and incentives</span>
    </div>

    <div class="loop-label" style="top: 78%; left: 78%;">
      <span class="t">Adversarial Testing</span>
      <span class="s">agent populations under operational pressure</span>
    </div>

    <div class="loop-label" style="top: 78%; left: 22%;">
      <span class="t">Evidence & Fixes</span>
      <span class="s">reported, prioritised, and fed back into the system</span>
    </div>

    <div class="loop-center">Iterative feedback loop</div>
  </div>
  <figcaption>
    outputs:<strong>&nbsp;safety reports</strong> · <strong
      >test infrastructure · agent runtimes</strong
    >
  </figcaption>
</figure>
